    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Screamer Streamers is a roguelike horror-action game about streaming chaos live.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You’re not just surviving a nightmare — you’re broadcasting it.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STREAM TO SURVIVE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Go live.</strong><br><strong>Dive in.</strong><br><strong>Fight back.</strong><br><strong>Keep the audience engaged.</strong><br>Because <strong>if the stream dies, you’re done.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>YOUR PHONE IS THE GAME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your phone to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stream</strong> in real time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Track</strong> objectives</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>React</strong> to sudden events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Handle</strong> modifiers, surprises, and chaos mid-run</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY THE RISK GAME</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Push forward</strong> for better content</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play safe</strong> and lose momentum</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adapt fast</strong> when the stream flips the rules</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LIVE PRESSURE, REAL CONSEQUENCES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay live longer and the run gets worse:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escalate</strong> events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stack</strong> challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trigger</strong> environments that react to you on camera</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HANDCRAFTED SETPIECES, UNPREDICTABLE RUNS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore levels built from handcrafted setpieces:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Keep</strong> strong pacing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deliver</strong> memorable encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stay</strong> fresh every run</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BUILD. BREAK. REBUILD.</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pick</strong> characters, weapons, and tools</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade</strong> your run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rethink</strong> your build when stream events hit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive</strong> by adapting, not by memorizing</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wishlist now</strong> and get notified when the show goes live.</p>",
